snippet.title: Clear Vision 4 - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
17+ NOT SUITABLE FOR CHILDREN! 
 
Your favorite assassin Tyler is back in the most brutal sniper game around.
Help Tyler get his hitman career back on track by making your way through tons of tailor-made sniper missions and build your arsenal of sniper rifles.
 
“ We have a young man that owes us money, he refuses to pay. We refuse to let him live.”

From the Eldring team!
